PERCEPTOR has succesfully brought NIGHTSHIFT outside of the trap and
now has him laying on the ground. There is still a piece of the dart
that the human shot into him still lodge in the upper thigh of his
beastmode. It continues to glow a dull blue color.

Meanwhile there is a dull rumbling sound down the tunnel behind
WINDLORD and PERCEPTOR and then a cloud of dust and dirt comes up the
tunnel. It would appear that there has been a cave in.
